  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 47-7-37.1, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO PROVIDE THAT PROBATION, POST-RELEASE SUPERVISION, OR SUSPENSION OF SENTENCE MAY BE REVOKED PRIOR TO ITS COMMENCEMENT IF A NEW FELONY CRIME IS COMMITTED PRIOR TO ITS COMMENCEMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
